"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802716","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-12-14","<p>The Ministry of Defence is investigating how best to deliver State Ceremonial and Public Duties in London. We are currently conducting detailed assessment studies to determine the best way forward.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood","118267","2017-12-14T17:22:54.59Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802716/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802716/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802716/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-12-07","Hyde Park Barracks","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, whether his Department has reversed its decision to sell Hyde Park Barracks; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","118265"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802717","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-12-14","<p>The Defence Estate Optimisation Programme which is delivering the Better Defence Estate Strategy is a 25-year programme which is forecast to save £140 million in running costs over ten years, rising to nearly £3 billion by 2040.</p><p>The Ministry of Defence is investigating how best to deliver State Ceremonial and Public Duties in London. We are currently conducting detailed assessment studies to determine the best way forward.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood",,"2017-12-14T17:20:04.733Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802717/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802717/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802717/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-12-07","Military Bases","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what estimate he has made of potential savings to his Department from (a) the better defence estate strategy and (b) the potential sale of Hyde Park Barracks.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","118266"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802718","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-12-14","<p>The Ministry of Defence is investigating how best to deliver State Ceremonial and Public Duties in London. We are currently conducting detailed assessment studies to determine the best way forward.</p>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood","118265","2017-12-14T17:22:54.653Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802718/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802718/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/802718/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-12-07","Hyde Park Barracks","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, whether he has any plans (a) to sell Hyde Park barracks and (b) to relocate the Household Cavalry and the location for state ceremonial and public duties in London.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","118267"
